      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) الْغَضَبُ مِفْتَاحُ كُلِّ شَرٍّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, fro Dawood Bin Farqad who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup style=\"font-weight: normal\">asws</sup> said: ‘The anger is a key to every evil’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from Yunus from Dawud ibn Farqad who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘Anger is the key to all evil.’” "
        ]
